char *a[1005];

int bsearch(char *a[],int len,char *val)
{
    int mid;
    int first=0;
    int last=len-1;

    while(first<=last)
    {
        mid=(first+last)/2;
        if(strcmp(a[mid], val)==0)
        {
            return 1;
        }
        else if(strcmp(a[mid], val)<0)
           { first=mid+1;
        }
        else
        last=mid-1;
    }
    return 0;
}
